---
const missionImg = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466637574441-749b8f19452f?w=1100&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop";
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- photo + sticker -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img src={missionImg}
             alt="A vendor handing a plate across the order window."
             class="w-full block"
             style="aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(42,26,14,0.18);" />
        <div class="sticker absolute"
             style="right: -16px; bottom: 36px; transform: rotate(-3deg); min-width: 180px;">
          <span class="accent-script block leading-none mb-1" style="font-size: 22px;">est. 2025</span>
          <div class="display-lg" style="font-size: 40px; line-height: 1; color: var(--color-ink);">501(c)(3)</div>
          <div class="font-sans font-semibold text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mt-1" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
            Tax-deductible
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- copy -->
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our mission</span>
        <h2 class="h2-display" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
          Vendors bring the food. We bring the wider doorway.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-[19px] leading-[1.55] mb-4" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
          Mobile food is how Hawai‘i feeds itself outside the restaurants — at the
          beach, after work, on the way home, between shifts. Behind every truck and
          popup is a person with a reason and a recipe.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-[19px] leading-[1.55] mb-8" style="color: var(--color-ink-soft);">
          The Foundation tells those stories — long-form — and builds the practical
          tools that go alongside: a marketing course for vendors, and the
          unglamorous advocacy work that smooths the road for everyone trying to do
          this for a living.
        </p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn btn-ghost">Read the full story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
